<!--What is CourtBot-->
<section>
  <div class="container text-center" id="whatIsCourtBot">
    <main>
      <h2>What is CourtBot?</h2>
      <p class="lead">PTA meetings, doctor's appointments, even court dates when life gets hectic, reminders help. COURTBOT is a text-message app that helps keep everything on track. After cases are booked, clients can text their case number to COURTBOT to receive automatic reminders of court dates.</p>
  </main>
  </div>
</section>
<!--Why CourtBot-->
<section class="CBLtBgClr">
  <div class="container text-center" id="whyCourtBot">
    <article>
      <h2>Why CourtBot?</h2>
      <h4>LESS BUREAUCRACY</h4>
      <p class="lead">Around 25% of the people in Tulsa County Jail are waiting for their cases to be heard, costing taxpayers up to $25,000 per day. Research shows that reminders work. More small fines are collected, and jail space is freed for more serious offenders.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <h4>FEWER FINES</h4>
      <p class="lead">Failure-to-appear and failure-to-pay fines can quickly snowball, especially for those living paycheck-to-paycheck. CourtBot helps clients avoid mistakes that burden them and the criminal justice system. Government done well can help.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
